extends baseEmail

block content
  h1 Your Monthly Summary
  p Hi #{firstName},
  p Here's a summary of your spending for the past month. We've compiled your transactions to help you understand your financial patterns.

  h2 Summary Highlights:
  p - Total Spent: #{totalSpent}
  p - Top Spending Category: #{topCategory}
  p - Budget Status: #{budgetStatus}

  table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation' border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0')
    tbody
      tr
        td(align='left')
          table(role='presentation' border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0')
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') View Full Report

  p Thank you for using Expense Tracker to manage your finances. We're here to help you reach your financial goals!
  p - The Expense Tracker Team